title: Stay Open For God To Do It His Way | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Stay Open For God To Do It His Way | Joel Osteen
description:
God's ways are higher than our ways. His answer may not come the way you were expecting, but His plan is exactly what you need to get you where you're supposed to be. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
